China to Build Solar Power Plants in Western Provinces

-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 
2011-04-01T09:46:52Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-31/china-to-build-solar-power-plants-in-western-provinces-ndrc-s-ren-says.html
(Corrects official’s title and spelling of his name in
second paragraph of story published March 31.)  China plans to build solar  power
plants  in Jiuquan in  Gansu province , in Hami city of Xinjiang
and west  Inner Mongolia , with the aim of achieving at least 1
gigawatt of installed capacity in each region, Ren Dongming,
director of the renewable energy development center under
the National Development and Reform Commission’s energy research
institute, said at a conference in Beijing today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Bloomberg News at 
 swong139@bloomberg.net  